msgid ""
"The options discussed above refer to the institutions listed in the "
"Institutions View. Most of the rows in this view are accounts. Right-"
"clicking an account name brings up an Account Options menu. The entries and "
"details for this menu are discussed at the end of the <link linkend="
"\"details.accounts.options\">Accounts Chapter</link>."
msgstr ""

